<section>
  <h2 id="a-few-other-observations">A Few Other Observations</h2>

  <ul>
    <li class="fragment"><strong>comments if you got &#39;em</strong> (code should speak for itself with meaningful variable names and legible formatting; if it doesn&#39;t, use comments)</li>
    <li class="fragment"><strong>you probably shouldn&#39;t hardcode</strong> every single object in <code>generateCards</code></li>
    <li class="fragment"><strong>commit often</strong>! it&#39;d be great to commit by feature. (even better to branch per feature, but we&#39;re not there yet)</li>
    <li class="fragment"><strong>it&#39;s not a complete blackjack game</strong> by any means (what about quitting? doubling down? etc.)&#8230; feel free to implement these if you like!</li>
  </ul>
</section>

